text: Alfheim is an old Norse place-name. It may refer to: *Álfheimr, home of the elves in Norse mythology *Álfheimr (region), a historical region *Alfheim Mountain Cabin, a cabin in Sunndal, Norway *Alfheim stadion, a football stadium in Tromsø, Norway Alfheim is also the name of individual areas in several Norwegian municipalities. An area named Alfheim may be found in: *Asker *Grue *Halden *Lier *Tromsø
title: Alfheim (disambiguation)
